RUNELF_BG(1)

NAME
    runelf_bg - run an ELF program in the background

SYNOPSIS
    runelf_bg path [arg ...]

DESCRIPTION
    runelf_bg is a shell built-in that starts an ext2 ELF program as a
    reattachable background job. The job can later be listed with jobs,
    reattached with fg, or terminated with kill.

    bg is an alias for runelf_bg.

SEE ALSO
    bg(1), jobs(1), fg(1), kill(1)
